The files in this module define the common icinga objects as well as some classes to help monitoring target servers.

# Icinga check commands
manifests/commands/commands.pp
manifests/commands/*.pp

# Icinga objects
manifests/contacts.pp
manifests/contactgroups.pp
manifests/hostsgroups.pp
manifests/timeperiods.pp

Icinga hosts and services are defined in the following places:
monitoring::target - Generic OS monitoring
monitoring::postgres - postgres nrpe check
monitoring::mysql - mysql nrpe check
monitoring::oae - OAE health checks
monitoring::cle - CLE health checks

# Target servers
manifests/target.pp

# Service-specific targets
manifests/target/*.pp